 data, computer models, and observations to predict storms, temperature patterns, and climate trends.", "Botany is the scientific study of plants, including their physiology, structure, genetics, ecology, and classification. It is essential for agriculture, pharmacology, and understanding global carbon cycles."], "scores": [0.8327245462685783, 0.8119741379623222, 0.62455872115441, 0.6094482298862649, 0.5897634824583103], "model_name": "bge-base", "document_ids": ["Astrophysics", "Astronomy", "Geology", "Meteorology", "Botany"]}}